  "system": {
    "biography": {
      "value": "<p>Rockborn transition Stone Nephilim from obstacles into active threats. Crushing Slam builds toward Grapple and the ongoing damage that Grapple provides. Stone Grip makes escape from that Grapple genuinely difficult. A summoner who wants something held in place while allies deal with it elsewhere will find a Rockborn with a Grappled target the most efficient delivery mechanism available at this tier.</p>"
