    "tactics": "",
    "attacksNotes": "<ul>\n<li><strong>Crushing Slam [Combat]:</strong> Melee attack (Agi 2 + Melee Combat 5), Reach: 10 ft\n<ul>\n<li><em>Margin 1:</em> 10 damage (Large, standard: 8 + 2)</li>\n<li><em>Margin 2:</em> 16 damage (10 + 6 Str); target knocked Prone + Grappled; no save; Grappled target takes 6 bludgeoning damage at the start of each of their turns</li>\n<li><em>Margin 3:</em> 16 damage + Prone + Grappled + Restrained; ongoing damage increases to 10</li>\n</ul></li>\n<li><strong>Boulder Hurl [Combat]:</strong> Ranged attack (Dex 2 + Ranged Combat 1), Range: 60/120 ft\n<ul>\n<li><em>Margin 1:</em> 10 damage</li>\n<li><em>Margin 2:</em> 10 damage; target knocked Prone + Stunned until end of their next turn; no save</li>\n</ul></li>\n</ul>",
    "specialAbilitiesNotes": "<ul>\n<li><strong>Immovable:</strong> As Stone Kin.</li>\n<li><strong>Earth Bond:</strong> As Stone Kin.</li>\n<li><strong>Powerful Build.</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Stone Grip:</strong> Creatures Grappled by the Rockborn add 1 to both dice on Athletics, Acrobatics, and Might checks to escape. The stone hand does not tire.</li>\n</ul>",
    "reactionsNotes": "<ul>\n<li><strong>Stone Skin [Reaction]:</strong> Once per round when hit by a physical attack, reduce incoming damage by 4.</li>\n</ul>",
